Visit stayteen.org
or abcfamily.com
for more information.

24:03.127 --> 24:05.627
How far apart are
the contractions now?

24:05.627 --> 24:09.877
Um, they are many,
many minutes apart.

24:09.877 --> 24:11.667
Many.
How many?

24:11.667 --> 24:13.917
Why don't you, like,
play some music
or something?

24:13.917 --> 24:16.047
Wouldn't it be nice to
hear some music, Kathy?
Yeah.

24:16.047 --> 24:19.627
Oh, my God,
I hope she doesn't
make it to the hospital.

24:19.627 --> 24:22.127
What?
It's like the birth of Christ

24:22.127 --> 24:24.337
and we're the
three wise women!

24:24.337 --> 24:26.997
Uh, it would not be
wise to have a baby
in the toy store.

24:26.997 --> 24:28.337
We have to
get her to a hospital.
She's what, 15?

24:28.877 --> 24:29.997
Hmm...

24:34.497 --> 24:36.087
I don't believe I did this.
I don't believe I did this.

24:36.087 --> 24:37.457
We saw your car,
so we drove in.

24:40.497 --> 24:41.297
No!
No!

24:43.047 --> 24:45.797
Hey!
Merry Christmas, guys!
What's going on?

24:45.797 --> 24:48.457
What's going on is
that Kathy's in there

24:48.457 --> 24:50.417
and she's having a baby
and for some reason
the ambulance isn't here

24:50.417 --> 24:52.047
and we can't get our cars
out of this parking lot.

24:52.047 --> 24:53.997
And now
you can't either!

24:53.997 --> 24:56.757
Hmm.
Never drove
here before.

24:56.757 --> 24:58.047
Yeah. Me neither.
(CELL PHONE RINGING)

25:00.957 --> 25:02.257
Where are they?
Sir, we're having
trouble

25:02.257 --> 25:04.207
finding Hedy's
Happy Holiday House.

25:04.207 --> 25:05.837
We don't have
a listing for it.

25:05.837 --> 25:07.917
Are you sure you don't
have an address?

25:07.917 --> 25:09.957
They're not even
on the way!
Oh, my God.

25:09.957 --> 25:11.047
No. There's no
address on
the building!

25:11.047 --> 25:12.457
Cross street?
I don't know.

25:12.457 --> 25:13.457
It's just blocks
from juvie hall.

25:13.457 --> 25:15.207
The old one
or the new one?

25:15.207 --> 25:17.297
There's a new one?
It's near the old one.

25:17.297 --> 25:18.957
All right,
we're working on it.
(TAPPING KEYBOARD)

25:18.957 --> 25:19.587
Are you anywhere
near the stockyard?

25:19.587 --> 25:21.167
The what?

25:21.167 --> 25:24.127
I think I see
the stockyard.

25:24.127 --> 25:26.497
Was there an
ambulance or not?
Uh...

25:26.497 --> 25:28.047
They're working on it.

25:28.047 --> 25:30.087
Just look at this place!

25:30.087 --> 25:33.207
Oh, dear.
I can't have
a baby in here.

25:33.207 --> 25:35.167
I'm going to be
in so much trouble
with my parents

25:35.167 --> 25:36.417
and with her parents.

25:36.417 --> 25:38.167
(LAUGHING)

25:38.167 --> 25:41.417
